text:
February 1, 2017 10:00pm EST February 1, 2017 9:49pm EST Thon getting it done on defence. NBA Australia 
Published on Feb. 1, 2017 
Feb. 1, 2017 
Thon Maker made his third start of the season today and the rookie is making the most of his opportunity, with some huge plays on the defensive end.

Coach Jaosn Kidd is showing plenty of faith in Maker, gradually increasing his minutes and role as the season goes on.
